                <p class="intro-text">
                    *materializes on stage in a shimmer of green light*
                    <br><br>
                    "Greetings, Earth-entities! I am Zlorp from Glorbox-7. Your 'comedy' customs are... perplexing. But I shall attempt this 'humor' protocol!"
                </p>

                <div class="joke">
                    <div class="joke-number">🛸 Opening Observation</div>
                    <div class="joke-text">
                        I have studied your planet for 3.7 solar cycles. One question persists: <span class="punchline">Why do you have a "snooze button" on your alarm devices? On Glorbox-7, if you need awakening, we simply telepathically scream until the task is complete!</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="joke">
                    <div class="joke-number">🛸 Human Tech Failures</div>
                    <div class="joke-text">
                        Your "smartphones" are... intriguing. On Glorbox-7, communication devices read thoughts instantly. Yours? <span class="punchline">Require "updates" that last longer than planetary orbits, and still autocorrect 'ducking' to something illogical! Why not evolve telepathy? Or at least tentacles for better typing?</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="joke">
                    <div class="joke-number">🛸 Traffic Logic</div>
                    <div class="joke-text">
                        Earth traffic systems are fascinating! You have "rush hour" where nobody rushes. <span class="punchline">You sit in metal boxes, breathing exhaust, to travel at speeds our larvae could surpass. Perhaps rename it "Stationary Suffering Hour"?</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="joke">
                    <div class="joke-number">🛸 Closing Thoughts</div>
                    <div class="joke-text">
                        I am learning that Earth humor comes from... pointing out the absurd? <span class="punchline">But everything here IS absurd! This should be the easiest comedy in seven galaxies!</span>
                        <br><br>
                        Thank you for tolerating my confusion. I shall return to Glorbox-7 now to file my report: "Earth - Lovably Illogical."
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

